## Overseer of Secrets

Manager to store your emails and passwords with the ability to view, delete, and add as many as you wish!

All passwords are stored locally within the installation folder.

### Downloads

#### On Linux: 

Download: https://github.com/thelazybastard/overseer-of-secrets/releases/download/v1.0.0/overseer-of-secrets
Run this in the terminal: 
chmod +x ./overseer-of-secrets
./overseer-of-secrets

#### On Windows:

Download: https://github.com/thelazybastard/overseer-of-secrets/releases/download/v1.0.0/overseer-of-secrets.exe
Run the exe file!

